config BR2_PACKAGE_SMARC_SAL28_UBOOT_UPDATE
	bool "SMARC sAL28 Uboot Update"
	help
	  When selected the bootloader update package is built. This contains all
          binary image blobs required for bootloader and RCW update as well as
          the installation script that copies any of these data to its appropriate
          storage.
          The update package is stored as a FIT image. The installation script herein
          is sourced from u-boot CLI
          source ${loadaddr}:install

